21. Bb1
{ Sacrificing the knight to open up lines for the bishop. We'll conclude the trainable line here, as analyzing this complex position could take a while.   But after  21...exf3  22.Bxf6  gxf6  23.Qxh7+  Kf8  24.Bf5  Be6  25.Rfe1  , despite Black’s extra bishop, the position is an absolute mess with Black’s king struggling to find safety. }
